    Interface Description
    MMSClientHandler.PollingResponseCallback

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MMSClientHandler
    It is an object that can communicate to MMS through HTTP and send or receive messages of other objects.
    MMSConfiguration
    It is an object that contains values for setting MMSClientHandler and SecureMMSClientHandler.
    MMSGeoInfoReporter
    It is an object that processes geo-information and registers it to MMS.
    SecureMMSClientHandler
    This handler helps client communicate to MMS over HTTPS.
